nrigorous evaluation metrics for this new research problem. Comprehensive\nexperiments demonstrate the superiority of our model; several valuable\nobservations are also revealed to facilitate future research in multi-modal\nmedia manipulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 16:20:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
