 well as GDP's decomposition into its various components and\nconcluded that these suddenly forced savings do not fit traditional economic\ntheories of savings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 16:44:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
