died by the\nproposed GKS-UGKWP, which validates the method for polydisperse gas-particle\nsystem in the supersonic case, where the dynamic evolution process of the\nparticle cloud is investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 09:13:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-10"}
